February 19 - Issue #86


Over the weekend, the press further digested special counsel Robert Mueller=
's indictment of 13 Russians in connection with their massive, multimillion=
-dollar effort to undermine our democracy (https://www.nytimes.com/2018/02/=
17/technology/indictment-russian-tech-facebook.html). Here are the five big=
